com.optimizely.ab.bucketing

Class Bucketer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.optimizely.ab.bucketing.Bucketer

  • @Immutable
public class Bucketer
extends java.lang.Object
    Default Optimizely bucketing algorithm that evenly distributes users using the Murmur3 hash of some provided identifier.

    The user identifier must be provided in the first data argument passed to bucket(Experiment, String) and must be non-null and non-empty.

    See Also:
    MurmurHash
